tasks.description:
Fix 5 bugs found post-merge in PR#40 (ocma/albaconnect-worker-schedule):
(1) EXTRACT(DOW FROM start_at) must use AT TIME ZONE from schedule_timezone column — UTC DOW != Seoul local DOW for jobs around midnight;
(2) Overnight shift avail_from/avail_to string comparison broken — 22:00-06:00 is never matched because 06:00 < 22:00 lexicographically; fix: if avail_from > avail_to (overnight), split into two conditions;
(3) POST /workers/schedule DELETE+INSERT → use INSERT...ON CONFLICT (worker_id, day_of_week) DO UPDATE SET start_time=...,end_time=... for atomic upsert;
(4) GET /workers/schedule/:workerId is public — add auth middleware (must be own workerId or admin);
(5) Add 4 missing vitest tests: UTC midnight DOW boundary, overnight 22:00-06:00 match, concurrent upsert no duplicates, dayOfWeek Zod validation (reject 7/-1/non-integer).
